    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't find another one like this\u2014it's in absolutely pristine, showroom condition! I've babied this car from day one, and it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next adventure. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have\u2014come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
