      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty. It's honestly like it just rolled off the lot\u2014totally pristine and drives like an absolute dream! I've taken such good care of it, you won't find a single scratch or hiccup. It's perfect for anyone who wants that brand-new-car feel without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin, I promise you're going to fall in love with it!",
      "price": 43900.0,
