      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering its power through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Mechanical integrity is absolute: the dual-VANOS system has been meticulously serviced, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to ensure long-term structural rigidity. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from original suspension geometry and factory-tight bushings. Every mechanical component operates with surgical precision, offering the pure, analog driving experience that defines the E46 platform. This is a collector-quality specimen for the serious enthusiast seeking mechanical perfection.",
